Help Type: command
Command: wikigraph wikg://local/job/<job-id> resume

Purpose:
  Requeue one paused job.

Usage:
  wikigraph wikg://local/job/<job-id> resume

Arguments:
  <job-id>              Full job id or an unambiguous prefix.

Behavior:
  - Resume changes the job back to queued.
  - The transient worker is started if needed.

Example:
  wikigraph wikg://local/job/75d12f7e resume
